  "prompt": "Where do I get all episodes of dragon ball Kai in English?",
  "response": "You can find all episodes of \"Dragon Ball Kai\" in English through various platforms. Here are a few options:\n\n1. **Streaming Services**: Check popular streaming services like Funimation, Crunchyroll, or Hulu, as they often have \"Dragon Ball Kai\" available with English dubbing.\n\n2. **Digital Purchase**: You can buy episodes or entire seasons on platforms like Amazon Prime Video, iTunes, or Google Play.\n\n3. **DVD/Blu-ray**: Look for DVD or Blu-ray box sets that feature English dubbed episodes. These can be found on sites like Amazon, eBay, or local retailers.\n\n4. **Official Channels**: Sometimes, episodes are available on official channels or websites associated with the distributors of the series.\n\nMake sure to verify the availability of the English dubbed version on these platforms, as content can vary by region.",
